data.description: Just lowered so You don't Miss Out! If Seeing is Believing...Than Get Ready to be Dazzled! This Home has been Completely Remodeled from Top to Bottom. This Seller has spared No cost for Improvements and Upgrades. Let's begin Your home tour, notice that New Sparkling Siding and the Perfectly New Architectural Roof. Take Advantage of the high-speed internet, wired security cameras, and the house fully wired with cat6 and extend WiFi, additional WiFi coverage in the shop also.  Strategically redesigned the Deck is now Wrapping around to the front Porch, so You can Enjoy those Endless Summer Nights. Nothing is more Welcoming than the Feeling you will get when you walk into this home. Observe and Admire this Amazing New Modern Look. Note the Engineered Hardwood Floors, Energy Saving Windows, High Deep Cabinets and Top of the line Stainless Steel appliances. All Meal Prep is Easy on the Multi-Purpose Island that Completes Every Cooks need.  Original Classic Wood Beams have been kept outlining the Cathedral Ceilings. Bedrooms now offer the Max Comfort space needed with Practical and Useful Build- ins. Relax and Enjoy Either of the Spa Bathrooms which are HUGE and have double sinks and walk in Showers.  The Lower-level Family Room adds to more space and Convenience when hosting guest. Working from home is Simple with the lower-level Office Den or 3rd Bedroom you pick. Detached 2 Car Garage has also been Completely Revamped to offer almost ANY Woodworking, Gardening or Machine Shop Need. This 1200 Square foot Detached is Perfect for use in the Summer or Winter with a Duck-less Heating and Cooling System. Just Over 4 Acres of Gorgeous Rural land which has been cleared and shows the Meticulous Landscaping. No Stone left to Turn over and Only the Very best to show. This home Will Not disappoint you!  Call me today, I would love to show you this fantastic home! Seller is offering a Buyer 1-YHW
